      "writtenOn": "2021-01-26T12:58:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "let\u0027s create task right here:\n + avoids kick-task\n + avoids making transaction on Run slower (one fewer DS put), and fewer DS ops overall.\n\nEdge case:\n * If poke task (PT) creation succeeds but transaction on Run fails,\n   then still OK: the created PT task is still most likely necessary, and even if not, it doesn\u0027t hurt and is overall still more efficient than always creating KickPT -\u003e PT chain.",
