      "writtenOn": "2021-01-26T22:42:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good point. Actually, to avoid edge case, what do you think about adding a `deferredSideEffectFn` field to RunManager and we can execute those function after state transition transaction is finished successfully?",
