      "writtenOn": "2021-01-27T00:12:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "hmm.. I think it is technically not best effort because in the case of app crash or context expiring, the task execution is considered failing and should be retried shortly. I think the default is exponential backoff staring with 0.1s. \n\nBut true, if we are getting unlucky, we may introduce considerable amount of latency. So will change it to what you\u0027ve proposed.",
      "parentUuid": "2f642fa0_d1ef5e1d",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 244,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 248,
